         <prefercite>
            <head>Preferred Citation</head>
            <p>Meredith Johnson Autograph Collection, Accession #1082,
            Special Collections Dept., University of Virginia Library,
            Charlottesville, Va.</p>
         </prefercite>
         <acqinfo>
            <head>Acquisition Information</head>
            <p>This autograph collection, 1920-1934, 25 items, was a
            gift to the Library from Mr. Meredith Johnson of
            Charlottesville, Virginia (now a resident of Princess Anne,
            Maryland), on March 25, 1941.</p>
         </acqinfo>
      </descgrp>
      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>The collection contains autographed cards or letters to
         Meredith Johnson or Robert Underwood Johnson.</p>
      </scopecontent>
